    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Well-kept car in good overall condition that runs and drives well. It presents nicely inside and out, with the expected light cosmetic wear and signs of regular use for its age, but nothing out of line for a solid driver-quality example. A buyer should expect a dependable, enjoyable car that has been used and maintained, not a perfect showpiece, but a good honest example you can drive and enjoy.",
