    },
    {
      "id": "standard_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Clean overall with normal wear for its age, and it appears to be mechanically sound and ready to drive. It has been kept in decent shape inside and out, though it is not perfect and may need routine maintenance like any used vehicle.",
      "price": 33900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "good",
      "quality_value": 0.7,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers an affordable way into dependable transportation. It shows its age and is best suited for a value-focused buyer who wants practical utility at a low entry cost. A solid opportunity for someone comfortable with a well-used vehicle and looking for straightforward, economical ownership.",
      "price": 4995.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transportation, a project, or a handy spare vehicle. Priced to make sense, and represented honestly by a seller who believes in straightforward deals. If you want something inexpensive with potential, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly driver/project with a strong-running powertrain, responsive transmission, and plenty of usable life for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance. Not a cosmetic queen, but it has the kind of honest wear you\u2019d expect from a car built to be used, and it still offers dependable point-A-to-B capability with good bones underneath. Ideal as an affordable commuter, first car, or weekend fixer-upper for someone looking to get into a capable platform without spending big money.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Honest poor-condition beater with plenty of life for the right buyer. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This is the kind of car with real character\u2014the sort of honest, road-worn machine that still turns keys into possibilities. If you want a polished showroom piece, keep scrolling. But if you\u2019re looking for an affordable set of wheels with presence, practicality, and the charm that only a well-lived-in car can carry, this one has a story to tell. Perfect for a budget-minded driver, a project seeker, or someone who just needs dependable everyday potential without a big payment hanging over their head. It\u2019s a chance to get into a vehicle with soul at a price that leaves room to make it your own.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next owner, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking inexpensive transportation or a practical project opportunity. It shows its age cosmetically and mechanically, but it remains a compelling option for buyers who want a low-entry-price vehicle with plenty of potential. Priced to reflect condition and deliver strong value.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with plenty of life left for the right person? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a solid budget-friendly option for someone who wants dependable basic transportation or a great little project to tinker with. It\u2019s got honest wear, a bit of character, and the kind of straightforward value that\u2019s getting harder to find. If you want something cheap, usable, and priced fairly by a seller who believes in being upfront, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 9
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Clean, honest driver with strong bones and plenty of usable life left. Engine starts up willingly, pulls through the rev range, and the drivetrain feels serviceable for a budget-friendly daily, backup car, or light project. Suspension and chassis feel composed enough for around-town use, and it has the kind of straightforward mechanical layout that makes maintenance approachable. Cosmetically it shows age and wear, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you want an inexpensive car with solid core mechanicals and room to sort to your standards, this one is worth a look.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
